AJCR-08 EMBROIDERED NET 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Net Trouser: Twisted Silk Dupatta: Net Applique: Silk Color: Cream

Adorn yourself in the tranquil elegance of a white rose with this gorgeous attire, a breathtaking work of art. The alluringly embroidered Peshwas is magnificently beautified with ivory dori in an amalgam of light gold zari, surrounded by light gold cupped sequins, glistening like a dew-kissed camellia. Paired with an embroidered dupatta, serving as a veil of enchantment, this breathtaking ensemble becomes an impeccable choice for celebratory soir√©es.
